{"tid":580384,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好谷氣呀，老豆比自己d親兄弟呃","createTime":"2018-03-04T13:14:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-04T15:01:37.000Z","uid":57036,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0a0dbfc876b530772f7741a39162a05c68c48675","tid":580384,"uid":57036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T13:14:30.000Z","msg":"好長，但好心up，希望有心人睇曬，比d意見我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n是咁的<br />\n我阿嫲已經接近100大壽<br />\n但長年獨居同埋有病，係大陸住<br />\n我老豆有4兄弟，夾錢養阿嫲<br />\n兄弟A，係大陸住，包2奶，話自己無錢<br />\n兄弟B，都係大陸住，話自己無業，所以無錢<br />\n兄弟C，香港住，咬緊老綜，供緊錢<br />\n我老豆，香港住，草根黎只係未去到拎老綜，供緊錢<br />\n<br />\n4兄弟得兩個供錢<br />\n而筆錢係由兄弟B個仔管，即係我堂阿哥<br />\n因為佢都係大陸住<br />\n筆錢點用全部由佢話事<br />\n成日話唔夠洗，又話要請工人照顧阿嫲，又話要買藥油乜乜乜，又話過年工人要雙糧<br />\n要我老豆/兄弟C加錢<br />\n筆錢點洗全部由佢口講<br />\n<br />\n但大家有捐過錢都知<br />\n捐10蚊可能得1蚊落到窮人個袋<br />\n有9蚊都比d機構自己私吞左<br />\n<br />\n我老豆比錢番去養阿嫲出於孝心<br />\n但實際有幾多係用係阿嫲身上我真係好質疑<br />\n而我堂哥又岩岩結婚又生仔又話要供車又盛<br />\n<br />\n我同老豆講<br />\n有咩理由4兄弟得你兩個比<br />\n你點知會唔會比人落格<br />\n佢屌番我話養老母邊有得計咁多<br />\n仲話筆錢係佢佢點洗係佢既事<br />\n<br />\n為左供多d錢<br />\n佢夜晚仲打多份工<br />\n結果最近搞到入埋醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n比著係你，你點勸你老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6e4f6380e8d50b10f269bba1442e6df0635b450","tid":580384,"uid":43231,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T13:22:02.000Z","msg":"A同B都係廢老<br />\n管錢嗰個直頭紅十字會<br />\n叫你老豆睇緊啲盤數啦<br />\n唔係俾人恰到上心口唔出聲下嘛"},{"pid":"bfed473bde71ebf127ab2a9b30cbd7f1ba8cbce9","tid":580384,"uid":68202,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T13:25:49.000Z","msg":"你老豆係直情寧願比啲兄弟呃都唔願比少啲錢<br />\n咁固執嘅情況其實你好難阻止佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"777218c401de31b3c461e11a332a8ec0c8689667","tid":580384,"uid":57036,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bfed473bde71ebf127ab2a9b30cbd7f1ba8cbce9","tid":580384,"uid":68202,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T13:25:49.000Z","msg":"你老豆係直情寧願比啲兄弟呃都唔願比少啲錢<br />\n咁固執嘅情況其實你好難阻止佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T13:29:25.000Z","msg":"唉呢個先係問題<br />\n同埋死要面<br />\n自己都養唔掂<br />\n就話養老母係天經地義<br />\n又話兄弟點會呃佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9046d8b94a67c0f1943068190b109d194762a2a4","tid":580384,"uid":146631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T13:31:53.000Z","msg":"完全明白<br />\n想當年我阿嫲入左廠，我啲仆街阿叔要我老豆出埋車錢俾佢地去探老母"},{"pid":"4b2ed584357f18c4a62d241908e788cb767e7706","tid":580384,"uid":57036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6e4f6380e8d50b10f269bba1442e6df0635b450","tid":580384,"uid":43231,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T13:22:02.000Z","msg":"A同B都係廢老<br />\n管錢嗰個直頭紅十字會<br />\n叫你老豆睇緊啲盤數啦<br />\n唔係俾人恰到上心口唔出聲下嘛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T13:32:05.000Z","msg":"冇數睇呀屌<br />\n佢開個數話要洗幾多<br />\n我老豆就去過數<br />\n話洗左幾多幾多唔夠錢<br />\n就黎搵我老豆<br />\n全部口講，冇單冇據<br />\n我做細既，你教我點出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a74c50c516c339d37d7127a15bbd9986e75cf702","tid":580384,"uid":57036,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9046d8b94a67c0f1943068190b109d194762a2a4","tid":580384,"uid":146631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T13:31:53.000Z","msg":"完全明白<br />\n想當年我阿嫲入左廠，我啲仆街阿叔要我老豆出埋車錢俾佢地去探老母"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T13:35:27.000Z","msg":"醫藥費/車錢就事少<br />\n一次半次就算<br />\n而家我阿嫲係要&ldquo;醫藥費/生活費&ldquo;<br />\n我老豆都唔知要比幾耐"},{"pid":"46490b8591c700b15b8093dc16bf814d8bfb796e","tid":580384,"uid":49918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T13:40:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"757bbeac103015d991d7ab2aa375493dec66d110","tid":580384,"uid":57036,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"46490b8591c700b15b8093dc16bf814d8bfb796e","tid":580384,"uid":49918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T13:40:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T13:45:57.000Z","msg":"你講得岩，係冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但佢冇單冇據，好難令我信服冇落格<br />\n供錢唔平均係一個問題<br />\n另一個問題係我老豆充大頭鬼，養老母大過天<br />\n幾皮幾皮咁比<br />\n可能係自己平時死儲爛儲d棺材本黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab8e5580ff741d47afa2f1a7ad0ca46ac8052415","tid":580384,"uid":5971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T13:46:21.000Z","msg":"你老豆排第幾啊"},{"pid":"f8565f6249389513fd3782c9104c62cfb37edf65","tid":580384,"uid":57036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab8e5580ff741d47afa2f1a7ad0ca46ac8052415","tid":580384,"uid":5971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T13:46:21.000Z","msg":"你老豆排第幾啊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T13:47:50.000Z","msg":"最細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1b34147877e9937c19bdd0e8f24980f89c954f1","tid":580384,"uid":95397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T13:48:28.000Z","msg":"人性<br />\n所以親戚都係垃圾<br />\n<br />\n利申：感同身受"},{"pid":"fd71a217d43c9e99019b842f0e1ebe6fc316cae5","tid":580384,"uid":49918,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T13:54:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f3d46336f0f6afddf0a2936157d621f246c4ecf5","tid":580384,"uid":57036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1b34147877e9937c19bdd0e8f2